Ƙara yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Ƙungiyar Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Ƙasar Ingila tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Yawan kamuwa da cutar korona (COVID-19) ya nuna irin wannan ci gaba a kasashen Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Birtaniya, yana tabbatar da cewa ko da yake a matakai daban-daban, annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
A cewar kwarewar Italiya, dole ne kasashe, asibitoci da kuma cibiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya masu tsanani su shirya kansu don karuwar yawan marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 da ke bukatar kulawa, musamman ma a cikin cibiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na shekarar 2019, an samu rahoton wani mutum da ya kamu da cutar pneumonia da ba a san yanayin da ake ciki ba a birnin Wuhan da ke lardin Hubei, a kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar hana cututtuka da kula da cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta bayyana mai cutar a matsayin sabon coronavirus wanda yanzu ake kira Coronavirus 2 na cutar ta numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an kira cutar ta SARS-CoV-2 cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
A halin yanzu, kusan kashi 80 cikin dari na mutanen da ke da cutar COVID-19 suna da wata cuta mai sauƙi, wato kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba, kuma yawancin suna warkewa.
A kusan kashi 14 cikin 100 na shari'o'in, COVID-19 yana haifar da ciwo mai tsanani wanda ke buƙatar shiga asibiti, yayin da kashi 6 cikin 100 na sauran ke ci gaba da samun mummunan yanayin cutar da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan marasa lafiya da ke asibiti sakamakon COVID-19 ya kai kusan kashi 4 cikin 100.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta ci gaban da ake samu na cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Ƙungiyar Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da kuma Birtaniya (UK), kuma mun kwatanta shi da ci gaban da ke faruwa a lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya da na Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Kasashen da ke cikin EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya sun kamu da cutar COVID-19
Bayan China, COVID-19 ta ci gaba da yaduwa, kuma halin annobar COVID-19 a sauran duniya a halin yanzu yana bin na kasar nan.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Babban Daraktan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya bayyana cewa COVID-19 annoba ce.
A cikin mujallar Eurosurveillance 2020 ta 5 ga Maris, Spiteri da abokansa sun ba da rahoton farkon shari'o'in COVID-19 da aka tabbatar a Turai bisa ga ma'anar WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta ruwaito mutum uku na farko da aka tabbatar da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa 30 ta EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya (UK) tare da, tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an ba da rahoton mutum 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 daga cikinsu, 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Samun adadin da aka samu da kuma yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19
A Cibiyar Tsare-tsare da Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (CEPCM), ana sabunta adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samo daga tushen hukuma kawai kamar ma'aikatun kiwon lafiya, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da ƙasa da na yanki na ƙasashe daban-daban da kuma WHO, a kowace rana a karfe 8 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan wajen tantance yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya, da kuma kwatanta shi da na Italiya.
Don tantance yawan mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, mun ƙididdige adadin mutane da ke kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Birtaniya, ta hanyar yin la'akari da yanayin yanayin COVID-19, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma kwatanta yawan adadin da aka samu a kowace ƙasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8 na safe da bayanan Italiya na 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yadda cutar COVID-19 ta ci gaba a ƙasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya
A cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata, yawan adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya sun bi na lardin Hubei (China) gaba ɗaya (Hotuna 1).
A cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya, adadin COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu kafin ya ƙaru a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (ƙarin bayanai).
Wannan ci gaba ya kasance ne saboda karuwar yawan mutane da aka samu a Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya sun samu karuwar irin wannan adadin COVID-19 (ƙarin bayanai).
Hoton 2 ya nuna yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a kasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya dangane da bayanan Italiya na 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
A ranar 15 ga Maris da ƙarfe 8 na safe, wasu ƙasashen EU/EEA 15 da kuma Birtaniya sun riga sun ba da rahoton adadin adadin waɗanda suka yi kama da na Italiya kawai makonni 3 da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin mutanen da aka samu cutar COVID-19 suna ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya.
Canjin yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 ya nuna cewa annobar tana ci gaba da sauri a kowace ƙasa.
Wannan duk da cewa ƙasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban na gwaji kuma akwai bambance-bambance a cikin amsoshin sabis na kiwon lafiya na ƙasa, bambance-bambance a cikin ma'anar shari'o'i da bambance-bambance a cikin tsarin zaɓin marasa lafiya da za a gwada don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin kamawa.
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun ce kusan kashi 10 cikin 100 na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 suna bukatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da gaggawa a waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
A halin yanzu, ana samun bayanai game da karbar mutane daga asibitoci da kuma/ko cibiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya a EU/EEA don kashi 6 cikin 100 da kashi 1 cikin 100 na mutane (ba a gabatar da bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, ana bukatar a yi tattara bayanai a kai a kai don a kammala bayanan da ake samu a yanzu, wanda ya ƙunshi yawan adadin mutane da suka kamu da cutar da kuma mutuwar da aka yi.
Wani bincike da aka yi a shekara ta 201011 ya nuna cewa akwai bambanci sosai tsakanin yawan gado da ake samu a cikin cibiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya a Turai, daga gadaje 29.2 ga mutane 100,000 a Jamus zuwa gadaje 4.2 a Fotigal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe suna da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (baje 12.5 a cikin cibiyar kulawa da gaggawa da matsakaici ga mutane 100,000 a 201011).
An ba da tsarin tsarawa game da cikawar iyawar kulawa, tare da kimantawa ga kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya na yawan cututtukan COVID-19 da aka yi asibiti da haɗarin wucewa 90% na iyawar gado a cikin babban ɗakin kulawa, a cikin sabuntawar shida na CEPCM na COVID-19 RIGHT RISK.
Tun da yake har yanzu akwai wasu wuraren da ake samun cututtuka a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya, kuma asibitoci da wuraren kula da gaggawa suna yawanci da yawan yanki, ya kamata a kafa bayanai game da cututtuka da wuraren kula da gaggawa a matakin 2 na Tarihin Ƙungiyoyin Yankin Ƙididdiga (NUTS 2).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma halin da ake ciki a ƙasashen da ke kusa da ita sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya.
Saboda haka, dole ne kasashe, asibitoci da kuma cibiyoyin gaggawa su shirya kansu don ci gaba da watsa cutar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma da kuma karuwar yawan marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 da ke bukatar kulawa, musamman ma a cikin cibiyoyin da ake fama da ita a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin binciken da aka yi kwanan nan na ECPCM na nan gaba, hanzari, mai aiki, da kuma cikakken tsarin aiki na da muhimmanci wajen jinkirta yaduwar SARS-COV-2 daga tsarin hanawa zuwa tsarin ragewa, domin hanzarta da kuma farkon karuwar yawan shari'o'in ba zai ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci ba su fahimci, karɓa da kuma daidaita amsarsu, idan ba a yi aiki ba tun da wuri.
Ƙididdigar haɗari da sauri ta kuma nuna matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a da za a yi don rage tasirin annobar.
Akwai ɗan gajeren lokaci da kowace ƙasa za ta iya ƙarfafa ƙoƙarin ta na sarrafawa don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma rage matsin lamba a kan ayyukan kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba haka ba, tsarin kiwon lafiya na sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA na iya fuskantar ƙaruwar marasa lafiya da ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wadda ta haifar da cutar coronavirus ta 2 ta cutar ta shan numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV-2), ta yi sanadiyyar mutuwar mutane fiye da 3,000 kuma ta kamu da mutane fiye da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, wanda ya haifar da bala'in jin kai.
Kamar SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da dubban mutane da cutar SARS a shekara ta 2003, ana iya watsa SARS-CoV-2 ta hanyar wartsakewa kuma yana haifar da irin waɗannan alamun ta hanyar irin wannan tsari.
Koyaya, COVID-19 ba ta da tsanani da mutuwa fiye da SARS, amma tana da yawa fiye da yadda ake watsawa, kuma tana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa kuma tana shafar maza fiye da mata.
A sakamakon karuwar littattafai game da wannan cuta mai tasowa, wannan labarin yana ƙoƙari ya ba da cikakken bayani game da wannan bincike mai tasowa.
Za mu tattauna muhimman abubuwan da ke tattare da cututtuka, ilimin halittu, ilimin cututtuka, bincike, magani, tsinkaye da kuma rigakafin cututtuka.
Ko da yake har yanzu akwai tambayoyi da yawa da za a amsa, muna fata wannan binciken zai taimaka mana mu fahimci wannan mummunar cuta sosai kuma mu kawar da ita.
Bikin bazara a ranar 25 ga Janairu, 2020, ya sa mutanen Sin suka yi zaman lafiya har abada, kuma an tilasta musu su keɓe kansu a cikin mako guda da kuma sauran makonni masu tsawo saboda yaduwar sabuwar cuta ta kwayar cuta.
Wannan kwayar cutar tana kama da cutar coronavirus (CoV) wadda ta haifar da annobar cutar ta SARS mai tsanani a shekara ta 2003; saboda haka ne aka sake kiranta SARS-CoV-2 ta Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma cutar da ta danganta da ita ta zama cutar coronavirus 19 (COVID-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a birnin Wuhan kuma da sauri ta bazu ko'ina cikin kasar Sin kafin ta bazu zuwa kusan kasashe 50 a duniya.
A ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta haifar da fiye da mutane 80,000 da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19, tare da marasa lafiya sama da 40,000 da aka kwantar da su asibiti da mutuwar sama da 3,000.
WHO ta ce COVID-19 ita ce babbar magabcin jama'a, wadda ta fi ta'addanci haɗari.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin watanni biyu, an wallafa fiye da 200 a kan COVID-19, musamman a fannonin virology, epidemiology, etiology, bincike da magani, tun daga rahoton farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu 2020 wanda ya nuna jerin cutar, a ware daga marasa lafiya da yawa.
Wannan bincike yana nufin a taƙaice an samu ci gaba a bincike a kan wannan sabon batun da ke tasowa.
Da wuri-wuri za mu gwada COVID-19 da SARS da kuma wani cutar coronavirus, ciwon numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, annobar da ta barke a shekarar 2012).
