An kuma san masu karɓar bakunan tsakiya na wasu HCoVs.
Gano dabbobi masu gida yana da tasiri kai tsaye a kan hana cututtukan mutane.
Nazarin hulɗa da dabbobi da ke da CVD zai iya taimaka wa mutum ya fahimci CVD sosai.
Bisa ga bambancin tsarin furotin, ana rarraba CoVs zuwa nau'i hudu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV, da delta-CoV). Genus na Beta-CoV yana dauke da yawancin HCoVs kuma an raba shi zuwa nau'i hudu (A, B, C, da D).
Shaidar ilimin halittu ta nuna cewa kunyar gizo-gizo da kuma tsatsa suna da tushen asalin kwayoyin halitta ga yawancin alpha-CoV da beta-CoV, yayin da tsuntsaye sune babban tanki na gamma-CoV da delta-CoV.
A halin yanzu an san nau'ikan cutar mutum bakwai (HCoV).
Daga cikin su, HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 alpha-CoV ne.
Sauran beta-CoV guda biyar sun hada da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV), cututtukan numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV), da kuma SARS-CoV-2.
Aikin gano asalin dabbobi na cutar HCoV yana ba da tsarin fahimtar tarihin halitta, motsi da kuma abubuwan da ke hana ƙetare shinge.
Hakanan yana iya jagorantar ko sauƙaƙe bincike na mai karɓar bakuncin, matsakaici, da mai haɓaka SARS-CoV-2, tare da mahimman tasirin hana kamuwa da cuta a nan gaba.
An san dabbobi masu cutar ta CoV tun daga ƙarshen shekarun 1930.
A cikin shekaru da dama da suka gabata, an gano cutar HCoV bakwai.
An ware nau'in HCoV-229E na farko a cikin hanyoyin numfashi na marasa lafiya da ke da kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar numfashi a shekara ta 1966, sannan ya daidaita don girma a cikin layin ƙwayoyin huhu na WI-38.
Marasa lafiya da cutar HCoV-229E ta kamu da su sun nuna alamun sanyi na yau da kullum, ciki har da ciwon kai, taɓo, rashin jin daɗi da kuma ciwon wuya, tare da zazzabi da tari a kashi 10 zuwa 20 cikin dari na lokuta.
HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 duk suna nan a ko'ina cikin duniya kuma ana ganin suna yaduwa ne a lokacin hunturu, a ƙasashen da yanayin zafi ya yi zafi.
